dct_title_s: Plànols de les viles d'Andorra / by Cartografia Oficial d'Andorra; projecte i direcció tècnica àrea de cartografia i topografia ; disseny i realització cartogràfica: Benjamí Sabiron ; Carmen Sauer i Geogràfics ; disseny portada, Imatge GràficaGovern d'Andorra.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by countours, and shading. Set of seven sheets, one for each parish [parròquia] highlighting the main city. Includes on verso a brief textual overview of the Principality of Andorra and the parish concerned. Copyright: Govern d'Andorra Ministeri d'Ordenament Territorial. Includes inset maps of historic center [scale 1:2,000]. Ancillary maps [scale varies]. Shows parrish boundaries. Locates public buildings, tourist services, cultural sites,  leisure and sport facilities. Indexes, directories, and location map on verso.
dct_creator_sm: Andorra. Ministeri d'ordenament territorial. Àrea de cartografia i topografia
dct_publisher_sm: [Andorra la Vella] : Impresió Tallerlesl Grafics Soler, S.A., 2002.
